land during the Middle Ages."],"variants":[{"name":"Mànas","meanings":["Gaelic equivalent of   Magnus ."]}]},{"name":"de","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Pet form of any of the given names beginning with the letter <i>D-</i> (  compare  Jay   and   Kay  ), in particular   Dorothy .  It is also used as an independent name, and may in some cases be associated with the River Dee (  compare  Clyde  )."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. Magnus de Heaton married Magnus de Heaton I before 1108. They were the parents of at least 2 sons."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","1115–1180":"1115–1180","–Female":"Surnud","1115":"1115","before 1108":"enne 1108","1180":"1180","Mersham, Grimsargh, Lancashire, England":"Grimsargh, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","1115–1180":"1115–1180","–Female":"Kuollut","1115":"1115","before 1108":"ennen vuotta 1108","1180":"1180","Mersham, Grimsargh, Lancashire, England":"Grimsargh, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"–":"Décédée","–Male":"Décédé","1115–1180":"1115–1180","–Female":"Décédée","1115":"1115","before 1108":"avant 1108","1180":"1180","Mersham, Grimsargh, Lancashire, England":"Grimsargh, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Magnus de Heaton a épousé Magnus de Heaton I avant 1108. Ils ont eu au moins 2 fils."},"de":{"–":"Verstorben","–Male":"Verstorben","1115–1180":"1115–1180","–Female":"Verstorben","1115":"1115","before 1108":"vor 1108","1180":"1180","Mersham, Grimsargh, Lancashire, England":"Grimsargh, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Magnus de Heaton hat vor 1108 Magnus de Heaton I geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 2 Söhne."},"ht":{"–":"Desede","–Male":"Desede","1115–1180":"1115–1180","–Female":"Desede","1115":"1115","before 1108":"before 1108","1180":"1180","Mersham, Grimsargh, Lancashire, England":"Grimsargh, Lancashire, Angletè, Uni